run...UW-P goes on 16-2 run to lead 30-17...UW-P leads 60-49, UW-L goes on
19-4 run...Game tied 77-77, Clark (UW-P) hits lay up...Atchison (UW-L) cuts
lead to 83-82...Cropp (UW-P) 2 FT's w/ :10 left...Atchison missed 3 at buzzer.
